name: Trickstar Fes
desc: Special Summon 2 “Trickstar Tokens” (Fairy/LIGHT/Level 1/ATK 0/DEF 0). You can only activate 1 "Trickstar Fes" per turn. You cannot Normal/Special Summon monsters the turn you activate this card, except “Trickstar” monsters. If a “Trickstar” monster(s) you control that was Special Summoned from the Extra Deck would be destroyed by battle or card effect, you can banish this card from your GY instead.
